---
title: Golden Beyond Meat® Patties with Cream Cheese Smashed Potatoes and Aioli
description: Who doesn't love a good dip? Golden, mini Beyond Meat® patties and tender-crisp snap peas are extra delicious with a swipe of savoury garlic aioli.
